cs.SD, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with music semantics and audio-visual correlations between music and dance. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a likely category as the paper involves the analysis of audio and video data. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper uses a statistical computational model to learn semiotic correlations between music and dance. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the development and evaluation of a machine learning model. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the analysis of visual data (dance videos).
